## Page Objects

All page objects extend `BasePage` located in `tests/pages/BasePage.js`:
- `LoginPage` - Login page interactions
- `HomePage` - Home page interactions

### Updating Locators

Update locators in page objects based on your app. Use Appium Inspector to identify elements:

```javascript
// Android
this.usernameInput = 'id=com.example.app:id/username';

// iOS
this.usernameInput = '~username_field'; // accessibility id
```

